The Proposal: -
In organizing various cultural programmes and activities through the Department of Cultural Affairs.
It comes from the point of view of preserving and preserving folk arts that are disappearing in modern times.
Various festivals are organized by the government every year. Chaitra Navratri is a cultural festival.
Administrative approval has been granted under the above mentioned Government Decision for organizing the event.
Accordingly, it was under the consideration of the government to grant financial sanction to it.
The Government's Decisions:
The cost of organizing a cultural event, Chaitra Navratri, is Rs.
10,00,000 - (Rupees Ten Lakhs only) to be financed under this Government Decision
